message.text:
HAPPENING NOW: TamHunt 2025 Day 3 🌆✨

Narating na natin ang huling yugto ng TamHunt, IABF Tams! Hanggang sa pinakadulo, patuloy ang IABF Student Council sa pagbigay-sigla at pag-anyaya sa bawat Tamaraw na magsimula ng sarili nilang kwento kasama ang IABF SC.

Ito na ang huling pagkakataon para mabisita ang aming booth! Huwag kalimutang dumaan at maging bahagi ng pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025—sama-sama nating gawin itong alaala na hindi natin malilimutan. ❤️🙌

IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
Powerband: https://bit.ly/4gcoxgT
PDDC: https://bit.ly/46wHPcL

Bukas mula Setyembre 7 - Setyembre 12, 11:59 ng gabi

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto 
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Captured by MJ Astilla

message.text:
HAPPENING NOW: TamHunt 2025 Day 3 🌆✨

Narating na natin ang huling yugto ng TamHunt, IABF Tams! Hanggang sa pinakadulo, patuloy ang IABF Student Council sa pagbigay-sigla at pag-anyaya sa bawat Tamaraw na magsimula ng sarili nilang kwento kasama ang IABF SC.

Ito na ang huling pagkakataon para mabisita ang aming booth! Huwag kalimutang dumaan at maging bahagi ng pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025—sama-sama nating gawin itong alaala na hindi natin malilimutan. ❤️🙌

IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
Powerband: https://bit.ly/4gcoxgT
PDDC: https://bit.ly/46wHPcL

Bukas mula Setyembre 7 - Setyembre 12, 11:59 ng gabi

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto 
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Captured by MJ Astilla

message.text:
HAPPENING NOW: TamHunt 2025 Day 3 🌆✨

Narating na natin ang huling yugto ng TamHunt, IABF Tams! Hanggang sa pinakadulo, patuloy ang IABF Student Council sa pagbigay-sigla at pag-anyaya sa bawat Tamaraw na magsimula ng sarili nilang kwento kasama ang IABF SC.

Ito na ang huling pagkakataon para mabisita ang aming booth! Huwag kalimutang dumaan at maging bahagi ng pagtatapos ng TamHunt 2025—sama-sama nating gawin itong alaala na hindi natin malilimutan. ❤️🙌

IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
Powerband: https://bit.ly/4gcoxgT
PDDC: https://bit.ly/46wHPcL

Bukas mula Setyembre 7 - Setyembre 12, 11:59 ng gabi

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto 
#SoaringGreaterHeights

Captured by MJ Astilla

📣 𝗢𝗡𝗘 𝗗𝗔𝗬 𝗧𝗢 𝗚𝗢! 🚨

The wait is almost over—IARFA Volleyball Tryouts happen TOMORROW! 🏐🔥

👉 Don’t miss your chance! Register NOW by scanning the QR code and secure your spot on the court before it’s too late.

🗓 Date: September 14, 2025
🕛 Time:  12:00 PM – 3:00 PM (Women’s Division)
                        3:00 PM – 6:00 PM (Men’s Division)
📍 Venue: Sharief Mansion, near Quiapo, Manila

We’re looking for skilled, passionate, and team-driven players who are ready to represent IARFA with pride and excellence. 💪

🔗 Registration link:

https://docs.google.com/.../1FAIpQLSfPQqWDFt.../viewform...

⏳ The countdown is almost over—see you on the court tomorrow! 💛

#IARFAVolleyballTeam
